Susan May Pratt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susan_May_Pratt 0 Susan May Pratt (born February 8, 1974) is an American actress. She played Mandella in 10 Things I Hate About You, Alicia in Drive Me Crazy, and Maureen Cummings in Center Stage. Susan_May_Pratt ( born February_8_,_1974 ) is an_American_actress .
